In this paper,the relevant literatures of "forestry archives" in CNKI database have been selected as the research objects and the bibliometrics as well as the knowledge mapping has been employed for analysis.The research has found that the studies on the domestic forestry archives are showing the rapid development trend;the number of the core authors is less and the group of core authors has not yet formed;the journals publishing this subject mainly refer to the archives journals and the forestry journals;the main research institutions are involved in the agriculture and forestry universities,the forestry units and the archival management institutions;according to the analysis of the high frequency words and the high mediator central words,it is found that the forestry archives researches have formed three hot topics,such as the traditional archival research,the subdivided forestry archival research and the integrated forestry archival research;the forestry archives integration research that is formed by the reform of forest rights will still be the frontier research in the future.
经济地理学对于创新领域的研究,有力提升了经济地理学在社会科学中的学科地位。以"Web of Science"数据库为数据源,借助Cite Sp ace和VOSv iewer可视化分析工具对21世纪以来西方经济地理学中创新领域研究的总体概况,主要国家/地区、机构、作者及其合作网络,研究热点和发展脉络等进行探讨,分析了经济地理学创新研究领域的演进规律与主要特征。研究表明:2005年以来,该领域的研究进入快速发展时期并延续至今,《European Planning Studies》、《Regional Studies》是最重要的载文期刊。国家层面上,英国、美国、德国处于主导地位;研究机构层面上,瑞典隆德大学、荷兰乌德勒支大学、加拿大多伦多大学实力较强;核心作者层面上,Cooke P、Storper M、Bathelt H、Boschma R带领的研究团队具有较好的产出。该领域的研究可以划分为从新区域主义向关系经济地理学研究范式转变,以演化经济地理学为基础的研究两个阶段,形成了以"增长"、"知识"、"治理"、"网络"、"演化"为核心的五大聚类。西方经济地理学在创新领域研究呈现了与经济地理学的研究转向紧密相关、研究视角从地方化转向全球-地方、研究方法不断走向多元化、注重理论思辨和理论建构、对发展中国家的研究和理论框架构建有待加强等特征。
