在实体经济转型升级的新常态下,以大数据、云计算、物联网为代表的新一代信息技术正在迅速改变着人们的生活和方式,传统的科技情报难以适应新形势的信息需求。为此,科技情报工作应紧跟社会发展的步伐,以客户需求为引领,以大数据信息化平台建设为依托,以加快推进人才队伍建设为抓手,提升科技情报服务实体经济发展的能力。
Bibliometric analysis is applied to review the research results of resource room for learning in regular class of our country from 1999 to 2016. The results reveal: although the amount of research literature on resource room for learning in regular class increases yearly, the research is still at initial stage; the researchers of resource room for learning in regular class are staff of colleges or research centers from Eastern China. The core research groups haven't formed so far. The self-complied or adapted questionnaires are used to investigate the construction and operation of resource room for learning in regular class. The construction level of resource room fails to meet the requirements on the guide. The research hotspot centers on practice of resource room and is unsystematic. Heavy responsibilities should be shouldered to research the resource rooms for learning in regular class.
